# AndroidUtilFramework (Under Development)

A utility framework for android.
This repository contain some utility classes for android and some open source library.

https://github.com/IsseiAoki/SimpleCropView for Crop the images
https://github.com/QuadFlask/colorpicker to pick color
https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJava for Reactive Programming
https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxAndroid Android specific bindings for RxJava.
Examples of Run Time Permissions.

